<abstract><t>Mtrace is a tool used to troubleshoot issues in a network deploying Multicast service.  When multicast is used within a VPN service offering, the base Mtrace specification does not detect the failures. This document specifies a method of using multicast traceroute in a network offering Multicast in VPN service.</t></abstract>
